  name in WizardStep.Icon. Falls back to a "document" glyph for unknown names.
  Names supported: settings, percent, wallet, tools, users, package, layers, lifebuoy,
                   building, calendar, mail, lock, plane, tag, file, plus, link, list, shield, pin
*@
